code: @Test public void extractFirstSentence() {     String sentence = this.extractor.getFirstSentence("My short " + "description. More stuff.").     assertThat(sentence).isEqualTo("My short description."). }

@Test public void extractFirstSentenceNewLineBeforeDot() {     String sentence = this.extractor.getFirstSentence("My short" + NEW_LINE + "description." + NEW_LINE + "More stuff.").     assertThat(sentence).isEqualTo("My short description."). }

@Test public void extractFirstSentenceNewLineBeforeDotWithSpaces() {     String sentence = this.extractor.getFirstSentence("My short  " + NEW_LINE + " description.  " + NEW_LINE + "More stuff.").     assertThat(sentence).isEqualTo("My short description."). }
